description: Built to last through the roughest and toughest situations, the long-lasting Bolt rugged case provides your phone with 360 degree armored protection. A convenient kickstand and reinforced corners are just a few of the many awesome features of the Bolt rugged cell phone case. Even though the Bolt rugged case is made with high-quality, heavy-duty materials, it remains lightweight with a sleek, slim profile. The unique, multi-layered Bolt rugged case snuggly fits yours phone with flexible, precision-molded silicone that has precise cutouts to allow access to all features, buttons and ports. Features galore, the innovative Bolt rugged case is more than just an extremely durable case for your Phone. Fun and practical accessories include a strong lanyard hook for secure attachment, convenient built-in kickstand and versatile holster that swivels 360 degrees for added comfort. With all of this durability and all of these exciting enhancements,the Bolt rugged case is a high-quality and stylish cell phone accessory. The Bolt rugged case is available in a range of color combinations. FEATURES: • Constructed using sturdy thermoplastic polyurethane (TPU) and shock absorbing silicone • Practical built-in kickstand for hands-free viewing • Swivel holster clip included for extra versatility • Attaches to your device in seconds.
